\f0\fs36 \cf2 \cb3 #\cf4  plainwhite
\fs24 \
\
Simplistic jekyll portfolio-style theme for writers.\
\
\cf2 **
\f1\b \cf4 Demo
\f0\b0 \cf2 **\cf4 : \cf2 [\cf5 samarsault.com\cf2 ](\cf6 https://samarsault.com\cf2 )\cf4 \
\
